In re Resignation of Crist.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Crist (1994), 69 Ohio St.3d 1218.]

(No. 94-1068 Submitted June 15, 1994 Decided June 20, 1994.)

The resignation of John Allison Crist of Middletown, Ohio, as an attorney, Registration No. 0012401, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
